    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the high-revving F22C1 inline-four, delivering 240 hp with a linear power band and an 8,200 RPM fuel cutoff. The drivetrain remains factory-spec, centered around a precise, close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, the chassis retains its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and high-rigidity X-bone frame. Meticulously maintained with all factory VIN tags present on every panel, the exterior finish and interior upholstery exhibit zero degradation. This is an investment-grade roadster for the purist seeking telepathic steering response and legendary 50/50 weight distribution.",
